The Alex Jones Show
Thursday, 03 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Scheduled Guests
................

From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with film-maker, broadcaster and former broker and options trader Max Keiser. Keiser is the host of On the Edge, a program of news and analysis hosted by Press TV and also hosts Keiser Report, a financial tabloid, that broadcasts on RT.


Though not billed on the Infowars web site, Alex spent most of the third hour today talking with Lenny Dykstra.
